narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, but they should be able to self-motivate.

I would recommend these course for all students interested in documentary production, from beginners to advanced ones. And is always nice to share your ideas and materials with the class for discussion.
